{"type":"message","id":"c3ee689e","parentId":"56c355d9","timestamp":"2026-03-28T22:48:02.930Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No memory exists about Notion being set up or used for you. I’ve got:\n- Your **goals** (first income stream, AI/automation projects).\n- Your **tools** (Antigravity, OpenClaw, Telegram).\n- Your **style** (accountability-focused, no fluff).\n\n---\n**Question:** Where’s the Notion?\n1. **Is Notion already set up?** (Share a link or workspace name.)\n2. **Or is this a new setup?** (I’ll need you to authenticate/OpenClaw to connect.)\n3. **Or should I draft a todo list *here* first for your approval?**\n\nI won’t guess—**clarify the context**, and I’ll build it *exactly* the way you need. (No \"vibes\"—just execution.)\n\nExample of what I could create:\n---\n### **Ivek’s Todo List** *(Notion-ready)*\n#### **Active Projects**\n- [ ] **AI News Dashboard**\n  - [ ] Pull API data (Open-Meteo/wttr.in for weather context?)\n  - [ ] Build Telegram bot to push updates\n  - [ ] Monetization plan (sponsors? ads?)\n#### **Skills Practice**\n- [ ] **OpenClaw Skill: \"Weather + News Fusion\"**\n  - [ ] Combine `weather` skill with a news API\n  - [ ] Add to your workspace skills\n#### **Accountability**\n- [ ] **Income Stream Brainstorm**\n  - [ ] List 3 ideas (due: *Saturday*)\n  - [ ] Validate with potential customers\n---"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"75ItyuF3A","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","buttons":[[{"text":"Notion is already set up ✅","callback_data":"notion_ready"},{"text":"New Notion setup 🆕","callback_data":"notion_new"},{"text":"Draft here first 📝","callback_data":"draft_here"}]]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"mistralai/mistral-large-3-675b-instruct-2512","usage":{"input":15721,"output":413,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774738076964,"responseId":"c