{"type":"message","id":"cea5c71b","parentId":"db92bd10","timestamp":"2026-03-28T22:48:34.080Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Real talk:** I don’t have *unrestricted* access to Notion unless you:\n1. **Explicitly grant it** (share an API key or Notion integration token).\n2. **Or authorize OpenClaw** to connect to your Notion workspace.\n\n---\n### **What I *can* do *right now*:**\n#### **Option 1: Draft Here (Fastest)**\nI’ll create a **Notion-ready todo list** in markdown. You copy-paste it into Notion yourself. Example:\n```markdown\n### **Ivek’s Todo List** *(High Accountability)*\n- **AI News Dashboard** *(Due: Friday)*\n  - [ ] Integrate Open-Meteo API (weather context for news)\n  - [ ] Build Telegram bot to push updates\n- **Income Stream Brainstorm**\n  - [ ] List 3 ideas (e.g., AI chatbots, automation templates)\n```\n\n#### **Option 2: Build the Integration**\nIf you want *direct* Notion access:\n1. **Go to [Notion Integrations](https://www.notion.so/my-integrations)**.\n2. **Create a new integration** (name: *OpenClaw*).\n3. **Share your todo-list database** with the integration (use \"Share\" → \"Invite\" → paste integration name).\n4. **Send me the API key** (via `/exec echo \"YOUR_KEY\" > ~/.openclaw/notion_key`).\n\n---\n**Which path?** I won’t proceed without clarity. 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"mistralai/mistral-large-3-675b-instruct-2512","usage":{"input":16385,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774738109092,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8bffff0779ea11b9"}}
