ot Started | Consistency > intensity |\n\n---\n\n## 📁 Notion Setup Instructions\n\n1. **Create 3 databases:**\n   - `Daily Goals`\n   - `Monthly Goals`\n   - `Yearly Goals`\n\n2. **Add properties to each:**\n   - `Status` (Select: Not Started / In Progress / Done)\n   - `Due Date` (Date)\n   - `Priority` (Select: High / Medium / Low)\n   - `Project` (Relation — link to your projects database)\n\n3. **Link goals to projects** (if you have a separate projects database)\n\n4. **Weekly review:** Every Sunday, check alignment and adjust\n\n---\n\n**Copy-paste this into Notion. Done.**\n\nWant me to help you set up the databases with specific views (Kanban, Calendar, Timeline)? 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":19632,"output":721,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20353,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774738664489,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b5aa9fb35699dd66"}}
