{"type":"message","id":"7ef97422","parentId":"925e0e18","timestamp":"2026-03-28T23:02:37.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Done.** ✅\n\nYour Notion \"To-do list\" page is now populated with:\n\n### 📅 **Daily Goals** (5 tasks)\n- Focus Block (2-4h) — Deep work on ONE project\n- Learn by Doing — Build instead of watch tutorials\n- Capture Insights — Log 1-2 lessons in memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n- Review Alignment — Is today moving toward 12-month goal?\n- No Shiny Objects — Reject new ideas until current project ships\n\n### 📆 **Monthly Goals** (4 tasks)\n- Ship 1 Project — MVP counts, does not need to be perfect\n- Skill Deep Dive — Master 1 tool (OpenClaw, Telegram bots, etc.)\n- Income Brainstorm — Generate 3-5 ideas; pick 1 to validate\n- Review & Purge — Drop stalled projects; double down on what works\n\n### 🎯 **Yearly Goals (12-Month)** (5 tasks)\n- 1st Income Stream — $1+ from AI/automation work\n- Portfolio Built — 3-5 shipped projects showcasing skills\n- Foundation Solid — Coding fundamentals + architecture understood\n- Audience/Network — Build in public (Twitter/Discord)\n- Self-Trust Earned — Prove you can follow through\n\n---\n\n**Open your Notion page:** https://www.notion.so/To-do-list-331996240a6680268f4bc68282b2bba6\n\nIt's ready. Start checking boxes. 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"z-ai/glm5","usage":{"input":32132,"output":323,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32455,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774738937749,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b796cdb12117955a"}}
